    <item>
      <title>随着哈里斯势头渐强，亲特朗普政治行动委员会计划投入 1 亿美元进行广告宣传</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/pro-trump-pac-plans-100-million-ad-blitz-as-harris-gains-steam</link>
      <description><![CDATA[支持共和党人唐纳德·特朗普的超级政治行动委员会计划从现在到劳动节期间在七个摇摆州投入 1 亿美元做广告，民意调查显示，特朗普与副总统卡马拉·哈里斯的竞争将更加激烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/pro-trump-pac-plans-100-million-ad-blitz-as-harris-gains-steam</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 21:00:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国等待法院判决，可能推翻总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/thailand-awaits-court-verdict-that-may-topple-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国法庭本周将评估斯雷塔·塔维辛是否应继续担任总理，以此决定这个东南亚国家是继续照常运作还是陷入新一轮的政治不确定时期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/thailand-awaits-court-verdict-that-may-topple-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普向马斯克求助，试图重启总统竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-08-12/trump-turns-to-musk-as-he-attempts-to-reset-presidential-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是华盛顿版，有关首都的金钱、权力和政治的新闻通讯。今天，政治和影响力记者 Ted Mann 预览了今晚唐纳德·特朗普和伊隆·马斯克之间的对话。在这里注册并关注我们 @bpolitics。在这里给我们的编辑发送电子邮件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-08-12/trump-turns-to-musk-as-he-attempts-to-reset-presidential-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 20:29:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和以色列认为伊朗袭击的可能性“越来越大”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/us-shares-israel-s-view-iranian-attack-is-increasingly-likely</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官员们表示，美国认为伊朗袭击以色列的可能性越来越大，最早可能在本周发动，因为盟国领导人试图阻止全面战争，而五角大楼向该地区派遣了更多军队。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/us-shares-israel-s-view-iranian-attack-is-increasingly-likely</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 19:33:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰和俄罗斯计划在战火纷飞之际维持天然气供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/ukraine-and-russia-plan-to-keep-gas-flowing-as-fighting-rages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管在燃料跨境运输关键中转站附近战斗仍在继续，俄罗斯和乌克兰仍打算维持向欧洲输送管道天然气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/ukraine-and-russia-plan-to-keep-gas-flowing-as-fighting-rages</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 18:02:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>戈特海默呼吁为火车乘客补偿延误费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/nj-congressman-calls-for-rail-riders-to-be-reimbursed-for-delays</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年夏天，纽约市地区的通勤者在火车上和站台上被困了好几个小时，一名美国众议员希望，如果新泽西州交通局的乘客因美国铁路公司的服务中断而遭遇长时间延误，他们能够得到补偿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/nj-congressman-calls-for-rail-riders-to-be-reimbursed-for-delays</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 17:42:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏丹和平谈判陷入僵局，军队参与度不明</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/sudan-war-peace-talks-in-limbo-with-army-s-participation-uncertain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国斡旋下旨在结束苏丹内战的谈判即将开始的两天前，目前仍不清楚苏丹军队是否会参加，这给达成停战协议的前景蒙上了一层阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/sudan-war-peace-talks-in-limbo-with-army-s-participation-uncertain</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 16:11:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基确认占领大片俄罗斯领土</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/zelenskiy-confirms-capture-of-swathe-of-russian-territory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基首次公开证实其军队已占领大片俄罗斯领土，并称此次行动是为了保护该国边境地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/zelenskiy-confirms-capture-of-swathe-of-russian-territory</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 15:57:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国金融官员在领导人政策会议后前往中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/us-financial-officials-head-to-china-after-leaders-policy-meet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，美国和中国的高级经济官员将在上海举行会谈，这是中国领导人在每五年一次的峰会上阐述长期经济优先事项以来，双方首次会晤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/us-financial-officials-head-to-china-after-leaders-policy-meet</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 15:35:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国称斯塔默不同意马斯克关于言论自由的言论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/uk-says-starmer-disagrees-with-elon-musk-post-about-free-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 的发言人表示，他“完全不同意”改革英国党领袖奈杰尔·法拉奇 (Nigel Farage) 在网上发表的、得到埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 支持的言论，这是首相办公室在八天内第二次反驳这位亿万富翁的言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/uk-says-starmer-disagrees-with-elon-musk-post-about-free-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 11:16:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
